           move      rr-cod-fnt           to   m-gen-grf-cod-arc      .
           move      spaces               to   m-gen-grf-mne-arc      .
           move      rr-num-pdr           to   m-gen-grf-num-prd      .
      *
           move      40                   to   w-all-str-lun          .
